            "Explore the specific challenges and considerations when applying emission line diagnostics to low-metallicity dwarf galaxies, and how the proposed methods in the main paper address these challenges.",
            "Evaluate the effectiveness of the alternative diagnostic diagrams proposed in the main paper, and how they compare to the methods discussed in the results.",
